  <h4>3. Add platform</h4>

  <p>You need to add the platform SDK to the project to run on the simulator or device.</p>

  <pre>$ cd /path/to/the/project
$ cordova platform add ios (or android)</pre>

  <h4>4. Run on the simulator</p>

  <p>The following command will run the application in the simulator.</p>

  <pre>$ cordova emulate</pre>

  <p>If the command fails, you are missing something. If you want a quicker solution, try Monaca with the following instructions.</p>
