<h3>Using Onsen UI for Websites</h3>

<div class="h3-wrapper">
  <p>You can use Onsen UI <a href="http://bower.io">Bower</a> module for a quicker setup.</p>

  <pre>$ sudo npm install -g bower
$ bower install onsenui</pre>

